high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on the bottles' side.
Grab a tomato off the table.
Walk to the front of the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge, then grab it out of the fridge.
Walk to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato in the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Pick up the apple close to the knives on the table.
Put the apple in the fridge. Take the apple out of the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Grab a tomato off the table.
Place the tomato in the fridge, then grab the tomato from the fridge.
Walk to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato and reheat it.
